snippet.title: CA v. BETTY BRODERICK (1991): Confesses on the Stand
snippet.description:
(1991) CA v. #BettyBroderick: Elisabeth "Betty" Broderick is being retried for the shooting death of her ex-husband and his new wife, Dan Broderick and Linda Kolkena Broderick. Prosecutors claim an angry and bitter Betty killed the newlyweds in a jealous rage after she and Dan's very public and brutal divorce, in which he reportedly tried to leave her with nothing.
